{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Riot Ride is an <strong>arcade car-combat</strong> game with <strong>roguelike</strong> mechanics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Drive a<strong> weaponized car</strong> through <strong>procedurally </strong>generated levels in a <strong>retro</strong>, <strong>Tron-like</strong> world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Collect <strong>blueprints </strong>and deliver them back safely while fending off a <strong>variety of hacked vehicles</strong> trying to end your run.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219600/extras/Main.gif?t=1736094031\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Endless play styles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Scavenge <strong>weapons</strong> and buy <strong>passive items</strong> from the shop to survive. Use them to <strong>customize</strong> your car <strong>endlessly </strong>to further <strong>personalize your playstyle</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219600/extras/Garage.gif?t=1736094031\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Challenging bosses</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Face <strong>increasingly difficult bosses</strong>, each with <strong>unique attack patterns</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219600/extras/Boss.gif?t=1736094031\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Perma death</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Play, die, learn, and repeat</strong> until you confront the<strong> final villain</strong> in a brutal showdown to finally break free from the simulation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219600/extras/Death.gif?t=1736094031\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play up to 36 levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use up to 17 unique weapons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fight 8 unique enemy types</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Face off 9 bosses</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If you die, you lose all your progress</p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Aspiring Rebel","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3219600/81ca820b12cbe19520d321fba47692d6742fe700.jpg"},{"name":"Detonation Day","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3219600/81ca820b12cbe19520d321fba47692d6742fe700.jpg"},{"name":"Caught In The Crossfire","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3219600/81ca820b12cbe19520d321fba47692d6742fe700.jpg"},{"name":"Nailed it","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3219600/81ca820b12cbe19520d321fba47692d6742fe700.jpg"},{"name":"Not So Laser Sharp!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3219600/81ca820b12cbe19520d321fba47692d6742fe700.jpg"},{"name":"Not Afraid Of Heights!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3219600/81ca820b12cbe19520d321fba47692d6742fe700.jpg"},{"name":"Great Air Show, Buddy!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3219600/81ca820b12cbe19520d321fba47692d6742fe700.jpg"},{"name":"Nah, I'm Still Moving","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3219600/81ca820b12cbe19520d321fba47692d6742fe700.jpg"},{"name":"Missed Me","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3219600/81ca820b12cbe19520d321fba47692d6742fe700.jpg"},{"name":"Buzz Kill","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3219600/81ca820b12cbe19520d321fba47